<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Welcome to SendIt, <%= name %>!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #2c3e50;
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0;
            background: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            margin: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><circle cx="20" cy="20" r="2" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/><circle cx="80" cy="40" r="1.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/><circle cx="40" cy="80" r="1" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/></svg>');
            opacity: 0.3;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            font-weight: 700;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 10px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            opacity: 0.9;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .welcome-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
        }
        .account-details {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .account-details h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #495057;
            font-size: 1.3em;
        }
        .detail-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .detail-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #667eea;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .feature-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .feature-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #495057;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .feature-desc {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
            padding: 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            border-radius: 15px;
            color: white;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: white;
            color: #667eea;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        .dev-section {
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .dev-section h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #3498db;
        }
        .code-block {
            background: #34495e;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            margin: 15px 0;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }
        .social-links {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .social-links a {
            color: #3498db;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .features-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üöÄ Welcome to SendIt!</h1>
            <p>Your packages are in good hands</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="welcome-section">
                <h2>Hey <%= name %>,</h2>
                <p>We're so excited you've joined SendIt! I'm Sarah from the customer team, and I'll be walking you through everything you need to know to get started.</p>
                <p>I remember when I first signed up - being able to track my deliveries in real-time was a game changer. Now I can't imagine going back to guessing when my packages will arrive!</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="account-details">
                <h3>üìã Here's your account info</h3>
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Your name:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= name %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Email:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= email %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Account type:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= role %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Joined us on:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= createdAt %></span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <h3>Here's what you can do with SendIt</h3>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">üì¶</div>
                    <div class="feature-title">See exactly where your package is</div>
                    <div class="feature-desc">No more guessing - watch your delivery move in real-time</div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">üó∫Ô∏è</div>
                    <div class="feature-title">Beautiful delivery maps</div>
                    <div class="feature-desc">Visualize the entire journey from warehouse to your door</div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">‚è∞</div>
                    <div class="feature-title">Accurate arrival times</div>
                    <div class="feature-desc">We'll tell you exactly when to expect your delivery</div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">üì±</div>
                    <div class="feature-title">Smart alerts</div>
                    <div class="feature-desc">Get notified about delays or when your package is nearby</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="cta-section">
                <h3>Ready to send your first package?</h3>
                <p>Your account is all set up and ready to go. Click below to jump right in!</p>
                <a href="<%= loginUrl %>" class="button">Start sending now</a>
                <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 0.9em;">P.S. Our mobile app makes tracking even easier - download it from your app store!</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="dev-section">
                <h3>üë®‚Äçüíª For our developer friends</h3>
                <p>If you're integrating with our API, here's a quick example to get you started:</p>
                <div class="code-block">
// Track a package
GET /parcel/track/<%= trackingNumber %>

// Update location (Driver API)
PATCH /driver/parcels/:id/location
{
  "lat": 40.7128,
  "lng": -74.0060
}

// Get user's packages
GET /parcel/my-parcels
Authorization: Bearer <%= accessToken %>
                </div>
                <p>We've got detailed API docs if you need more examples - just reply to this email and I'll send you the link.</p>
            </div>
            
            <p><strong>Need anything?</strong> I'm here to help! Just hit reply on this email or give us a call at (555) 123-4567.</p>
            
            <p>Happy shipping!<br>
            <strong>Sarah Johnson</strong><br>
            Customer Success, SendIt</p>
            
            <p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #6c757d;">P.P.S. Follow us on Twitter @SendItApp for shipping tips and occasional dad jokes about packages.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>¬© 2025 SendIt. Making shipping simple since 2018.</p>
            <p>This email was sent to <%= email %></p>
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#">Support</a> | 
                <a href="#">Our blog</a> | 
                <a href="#">Twitter</a> | 
                <a href="#">Instagram</a>
            </div>
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 0.8em;">123 Shipping Lane, Suite 100, San Francisco, CA 94107</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 